<h1>What good is happening in the world today?</h1>
<h2><a href="/">impct</a> is a home for sharing <a href="/">stories</a>, <a href="/t/news">news</a>, <a href="/t/tools">tools</a> and  <a href="/t/resources">resources</a> to create positive social impact.</h2>
